</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;">Previous post</th>
<td class="" style="">
<div class="plainlist">
<ul style="">
<li style=""><a href="Roman_Catholic_Archdiocese_of_Munich_and_Freising" title="Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Munich and Freising">Archbishop of Munich and Freising, Germany</a> <i>(1977–1982)</i></li>
<li style="">Cardinal-Priest of <a href="Santa_Maria_Consolatrice_al_Tiburtino" title="Santa Maria Consolatrice al Tiburtino">Santa Maria Consolatrice al Tiburtino</a> <i>(1977–1993)</i></li>
<li style="">President of the <a href="International_Theological_Commission" title="International Theological Commission">International Theological Commission</a> <i>(1981–2005)</i></li>
<li style="">Prefect of the <a href="Congregation_for_the_Doctrine_of_the_Faith" title="Congregation for the Doctrine of the Faith">Congregation for the Doctrine of the Faith</a> <i>(1981–2005)</i></li>
<li style="">President of the <a href="Pontifical_Biblical_Commission" title="Pontifical Biblical Commission">Pontifical Biblical Commission</a> <i>(1981–2005)</i></li>
<li style="">Cardinal-Bishop of <a href="Roman_Catholic_Suburbicarian_Diocese_of_Velletri-Segni" title="Roman Catholic Suburbicarian Diocese of Velletri-Segni">Velletri-Segni</a> <i>(1993–2005)</i></li>
<li style=""><a href="Dean_of_the_College_of_Cardinals" title="Dean of the College of Cardinals">Dean of the College of Cardinals</a> <i>(2002–2005)</i></li>
<li style=""><a href="Bishop_of_Ostia" title="Bishop of Ostia">Cardinal-Bishop of Ostia</a> <i>(2002–2005)</i></li>
</ul>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
