</dl>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:BenedictusXVI-2.JPG" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e8/BenedictusXVI-2.JPG/220px-BenedictusXVI-2.JPG" width="220" height="251" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e8/BenedictusXVI-2.JPG/330px-BenedictusXVI-2.JPG 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e8/BenedictusXVI-2.JPG/440px-BenedictusXVI-2.JPG 2x" /></a>
