</div>
<p>Pope Benedict is Grand Master of the following Orders: <a href="Supreme_Order_of_Christ" title="Supreme Order of Christ">Supreme Order of Christ</a>, <a href="Order_of_the_Golden_Spur" title="Order of the Golden Spur">Order of the Golden Spur</a>, <a href="Order_of_Pius_IX" title="Order of Pius IX">Order of Pius IX</a>, <a href="../Order_of_St._Gregory_the_Great" title="Order of St. Gregory the Great">Equestrian Order of St. Gregory the Great</a> and the <a href="../Order_of_St._Sylvester" title="Order of St. Sylvester">Order of St. Sylvester</a>.</p>
