<dd>1989 <a href="../../w/index-title=Augustin_Bea_Prize&action=edit&redlink=1.php.html" class="new" title="Augustin Bea Prize (page does not exist)">Augustin Bea Prize</a> (Rome)</dd>
<dd>1989 <a href="../../w/index-title=Karl-Valentin-Orden&action=edit&redlink=1.php.html" class="new" title="Karl-Valentin-Orden (page does not exist)">Karl-Valentin-Orden</a> (Munich)</dd>
