<dd>1992 <a href="Decoration_for_Services_to_the_Republic_of_Austria" title="Decoration for Services to the Republic of Austria" class="mw-redirect">Grand Decoration of Honour in Gold with Sash for Services to the Republic of Austria</a></dd>
<dd>1992 Literature <a href="../../w/index-title=Prize_Capri_S._Michele&action=edit&redlink=1.php.html" class="new" title="Prize Capri S. Michele (page does not exist)">Prize Capri S. Michele</a> in <a href="Anacapri" title="Anacapri">Anacapri</a></dd>
<dd>1992 <a href="../../w/index-title=Premio_Internazionale_di_Cultura_Cattolica&action=edit&redlink=1.php.html" class="new" title="Premio Internazionale di Cultura Cattolica (page does not exist)">Premio Internazionale di Cultura Cattolica</a>, <a href="Bassano_del_Grappa" title="Bassano del Grappa">Bassano del Grappa</a></dd>
