<li id="cite_note-BBC2006Doc-31"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-BBC2006Doc_31-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><i><a href="Sex_Crimes_and_the_Vatican_(film)" title="Sex Crimes and the Vatican (film)" class="mw-redirect">Sex Crimes and the Vatican</a></i> (<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/programmes/panorama/5402928.stm">an October 2006</a> <a href="BBC" title="BBC">BBC</a> documentary quotation:</span>
<blockquote class="templatequote">
<div class="Bug6200"><span class="reference-text">The man in charge of enforcing it for 20 years was Cardinal Joseph Ratzinger, the man made Pope last year. In 2001 he created the successor to the decree.</span></div>
