<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://twitter.com/Pontifex">Pope Benedict XVI</a> on <a href="Twitter" title="Twitter">Twitter</a> (Official)</li>
<li><i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/bishop/bratz.html">Pope Benedict XVI</a></i> at <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.Catholic-Hierarchy.org/">Catholic-Hierarchy</a>. Retrieved on 3 April 2010.</li>
</ul>
