<ul>
<li><i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.vatican.va/holy_father/benedict_xvi/encyclicals/documents/hf_ben-xvi_enc_20051225_deus-caritas-est_en.html">Deus Caritas Est</a></i>&#160;– encyclical <i>God is Love</i></li>
<li><i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.vatican.va/holy_father/benedict_xvi/encyclicals/documents/hf_ben-xvi_enc_20071130_spe-salvi_en.html">Spe Salvi</a></i>&#160;– encyclical <i>In hope we were saved</i></li>
